doc.previous: On visits to Commonwealth realms which share the same monarch as the United Kingdom reciprocal VIP aircraft of those countries are often used when transporting members of the Royal Family
doc.after: Air travel arrangements for the President are made by the White House Military Office and typically one of two customized Boeing 747 200B jetliners are used These aircraft carry the military designation VC 25A
